text: NPC: Oh noes! Let me have fun!
NPC: What a big ball? Have I drunk this much?
NPC: I just wanted to have some fun! I'm out!
NPC: Oh come on! I have invested so much in that festival!
NPC: Guess the party is over, now!
NPC: Let me go! Let me go!
NPC: Oow, that hurts like a hungover...
NPC: My noodles! Oh my god, my noodles...
